<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>AI4M Labs | ATLAS</title>
  <meta name="description" content="AI4M Labs builds ATLAS, an AI visibility intelligence system for destinations and brands." />
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #0b1020;
      color: #ffffff;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 1080px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 40px 24px;
    }
    header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 28px 0;
    }
    .logo {
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    nav a {
      color: #cbd5e1;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-left: 24px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .hero {
      padding: 90px 0 80px;
    }
    .tag {
      color: #60a5fa;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 56px;
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin: 18px 0;
      max-width: 850px;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      max-width: 720px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 32px;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #0b1020;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .section {
      padding: 70px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 32px;
    }
    .card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .card h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #93c5fd;
    }
    .muted {
      color: #cbd5e1;
    }
    form {
      max-width: 620px;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }
    input, textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      color: white;
      font-size: 15px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    textarea {
      min-height: 140px;
    }
    button {
      background: #60a5fa;
      color: #06111f;
      border: none;
      padding: 14px 22px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    footer {
      padding: 36px 0;
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 14px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }
    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      h1 { font-size: 40px; }
      header { align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px; }
      nav a { margin-left: 12px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <div class="logo">AI4M LABS</div>
      <nav>
        <a href="#atlas">ATLAS</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
      <div class="tag">AI Visibility Intelligence</div>
      <h1>Understand how AI systems see, rank and recommend your brand.</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">
        AI4M Labs builds intelligence tools for the new search landscape. Our flagship product, ATLAS, helps destinations and brands measure their visibility across AI assistants, LLM-generated recommendations and prompt-led discovery journeys.
      </p>
      <a class="button" href="#contact">Request a pilot</a>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="atlas">
      <div class="tag">Flagship Product</div>
      <h2>ATLAS</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">
        ATLAS is an AI Tracking & LLM Analysis System designed to reveal how destinations, brands and experiences appear across AI-generated recommendations.
      </p>

      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Measure AI visibility</h3>
          <p class="muted">Track whether your brand appears in AI-generated answers across strategic prompt categories.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Benchmark competitors</h3>
          <p class="muted">Understand who is being recommended, in what context and against which alternatives.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Identify gaps</h3>
          <p class="muted">Find weak spots in positioning, content and discoverability across AI-led search journeys.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Turn prompts into insight</h3>
          <p class="muted">Transform thousands of LLM outputs into structured, decision-ready market intelligence.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Built for the next era of discovery</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">
        As consumers increasingly ask AI tools where to travel, what to buy and which brands to trust, visibility inside AI-generated answers becomes a new strategic channel. ATLAS helps organizations monitor, analyze and improve that visibility.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="contact">
      <div class="tag">Contact</div>
      <h2>Request a pilot</h2>
      <p class="muted">Interested in ATLAS? Send us a note and we’ll get back to you.</p>

      <form action="https://formspree.io/f/xnjywdjp" method="POST">
        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your name" required />
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your email" required />
        <textarea name="message" placeholder="Tell us about your organization or use case" required></textarea>
        <button type="submit">Send message</button>
      </form>
    </section>

    <footer>
      © 2026 AI4M Labs. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
